    </alternatives>
    <type>auto</type>
    <previous>Tattha ca, doṇa, ko dhammo? Neva kayena na vikkayena, brāhmaṇiṃyeva udakūpassaṭṭhaṃ. So brāhmaṇiṃyeva gacchati, na khattiyiṃ na vessiṃ na suddiṃ na caṇḍāliṃ na nesādiṃ na veniṃ </previous>
  </note>
  <note line="78" original="māṇavakī (ka.)" reference-line="16" id="9">
